<html>
<head>
	<meta charset='utf-8'>
	<title>Thank You!</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Thanks <%= first_name %></h1>
	<p>Thanks for coming out to our conference. We coudln't have done it without you!</p>

	<p>
		Political activism is at the heart of any democracy and your voice needs to be heard. Please consider reaching out to your following representatives:
	</p>

	<table>
		<tr><th>Legislators</th></tr>
		<% legislators.each do | legislator | %>
			<tr>
				<td><%= "#{legislator.first_name} #{legislator.last_name}" %></td>
				<td><%= "#{legislator.website}" %></td>
			</tr>
		<% end %>
	</table>

	<% if(phone) %>
		<p>By the way, the number on file we have is <%= phone %>. If it's incorrect, please let us know so we can keep in touch!</p>
	<% else %>
		<p>By the way, we don't have a number on file for you, please let us know what is it to keep in touch!</p>
	<% end %>
</body>
</html>
